<h2 class="font_2">Who are we?</h2>
<p class="font_7"><span class="color_2">Welcome to the Nova Scotia League for Equal Opportunities (NSLEO). We are a provincial consumer organization dedicated to promoting the abilities of persons with disabilities so they may function as equals in society. We provide information and referral services to all Nova Scotians regarding disability issues and available programs and services.</span></p>

	
	
	
